<br>
Some of what you propose will take hundreds of man hours and is unlikely to occur soon, given the enormous burden faced by the developers in the next few weeks.<br>
<br>
Given that, you might consider prioritizing your list somewhat in favor of changes that require the fewest developer hours while solving the greatest number of problems.<br>
<br>
This is not simply a coding issue, i.e. not just the time to code the fix, but also includes balancing and likelihood of introducing additonal bugs.<br>
<br>
